    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263343>
    dc:description "PLATE 43. Clathrodrillia guadeloupensis, new species. Figs. 1 – 3: holotype, Grand Cul-de-Sac Marin, Guadeloupe (MNHN IM- 2013 - 7812). Fig. 1: ventral, lateral & dorsal views; Fig. 2: enlarged view of protoconch (not to scale); Fig. 3: apical view, V = varix, L = edge of outer lip. Figs. 4 – 5: paratypes. Fig. 4: juvenile specimen, Grand Cul-de-Sac Marin, Guadeloupe (MNHN IM- 2013 - 9051); Fig. 5: Hollandes Cays, Panama (P. Williams coll.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263343/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

